Interface IClassificationRun

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IClassificationInput

    public interface IClassificationRun
extends IClassificationInput
    Reflects the current state of a classification run.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      Date getCompletionDate()
      Returns the completion date of this classification, or null if the classification hasn't finished yet.
      Date getCreationDate()
      Returns the starting date of this classification, or null if the classification hasn't started yet.
      Boolean getEquivalentConceptsFound()
      Returns a boolean indicating if any equivalent concepts were found, or null if the classification hasn't finished yet.
      String getId()
      Returns the unique identifier of this classification.
      Boolean getInferredRelationshipChangesFound()
      Returns a boolean indicating if any inferred relationship were found, or null if the classification hasn't finished yet.
      Boolean getRedundantStatedRelationshipsFound()
      Returns a boolean indicating if any redundant stated relationships were found, or null if the classification hasn't finished yet.
      Date getSaveDate()
      Returns the date the classification results were saved, or null if the classification results haven't been saved yet.
      ClassificationStatus getStatus()
      Returns the current status of this classification.
